-- Ciel Textile Earns 40% of Profits From Asia, CEO Mayer Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-07-18T07:00:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-18/ciel-textile-earns-40-of-profits-from-asia-ceo-mayer-says.html
Ciel Textile Ltd. (FKL) , a company with
operations in Mauritius, Madagascar, India and Bangladesh, said
its activities in the latter two countries are the most
profitable, according to Business Magazine.  Asia “represents 27 percent of our turnover and 40 percent
of our profits,” Chief Executive Officer Harold Mayer told the
Port Louis-based publication.  To contact the reporter on this story:
